{"tid":291458,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"河南動物園棕熊「皮包骨」 園方辯稱牠年幼不會囤積脂肪","createTime":"2017-06-20T14:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T12:44:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac44c11b85680bc4b6fdc49a37fb125a202093e","tid":291458,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/ohw51q66cv.u3yzkVA2NHA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://l.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/GLB/2017-06-20/fa85caa0-557b-11e7-ad15-cbcfab740e9b__2017062013011043684.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fohw51q66cv.u3yzkVA2NHA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fl.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2017-06-20%2Ffa85caa0-557b-11e7-ad15-cbcfab740e9b__2017062013011043684.jpg&h=8feb4d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】河南省新鄉市人民公園動物園，因園內一隻棕熊「瘦骨嶙峋」，被質疑虐待動物。<br />\n<br />\n有內地網民前日在微博貼文及3張棕熊的照片，梳中的棕熊瘦得「皮包骨」，貼文者覺得牠看起來很可憐，隨即引發網民熱議，留言質疑園方虐待動物，或是讓熊挨餓。網友紛紛留言表示「這也太瘦了吧！」、「看著快餓死了」、「我家的狗都比牠重」等等。<br />\n<br />\n園方今日澄清，表示由於棕熊年幼，不會囤積脂肪，加上處於換毛期，所以才會讓棕熊看起來比較瘦小，強調飲食一切正常，從沒斷水斷糧。又指獸醫也會定期為棕熊做健康檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%9C%92%E6%A3%95%E7%86%8A-%E7%9A%AE%E5%8C%85%E9%AA%A8-%E5%9C%92%E6%96%B9%E8%BE%AF%E7%A8%B1%E7%89%A0%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%BC%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%9B%A4%E7%A9%8D%E8%84%82%E8%82%AA-045100020.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E5%258D%2597%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%259C%2592%25E6%25A3%2595%25E7%2586%258A-%25E7%259A%25AE%25E5%258C%2585%25E9%25AA%25A8-%25E5%259C%2592%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2589%25A0%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25B9%25BC%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%259B%25A4%25E7%25A9%258D%25E8%2584%2582%25E8%2582%25AA-045100020.html&d=0s4k466Ec1exW3L0JB69